It seems like the relationship between former Big Brother Naija pepperdem housemates, Jackye Madu, and Khafi Kareem is no longer cordial. During a Question and Answer session Jackye hosted on her Instagram page, she came out with honest answers which has revealed that there might be a strain in her relationship with Khafi. Recall that both were good buddies in the house. A follower asked the ‘Tech queen’ if she was still friends with Khafi, and her response seems as one who still holds grudges against the latter. “I don’t like snakes”, she noted. When another follower asked if is still friends with Mike Edwards, Jackye responded with a smiley that expressed her uncertainty. See screenshots below: 